_sText:
Thank you for downloading our map!

To install:
You extract the WINRAR.ZIP file to wherever you like.
Locate the hoejhus11_[kp].bsp file which you then copy to C/:Program Files (x86)/Steam/Steamapps/USERNAME/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps.
Exit the folder and play CS:S!
Have fun & enjoy!


BANANO-MANO.COM
The team
